title: JsonEditor
description: The JsonEditor Component Provides a JSON Editor.

body.raw:
## Import

```js
import { JsonEditor } from '@incmix/ui'
```

## Usage

Here's a basic usage example of the `JsonEditor` component:

```tsx
const usedJsonString = useJsonString({})
<JsonEditor placeholder="Basic usage" usedJsonString={usedJsonString} />
```
